    "In fact, p(R z 1 i 0) = p(Q i 0) + z 1 K (note that the side length of each Q i 0 is equal to 1 K.) Continuing in the same fashion, each rectangle R z 1 i 0 naturally partitions into subcubes Q z 1 i 0,i 1 and in each of these subcubes we consider the rectangles R z 1,z 2 i 0,i 1 with principal vertices at in the rescaled lattice1 KM 1 K Ref + p(Q z 1 i 0,i 1).",
    "There are two details to keep in mind.",
